      "writtenOn": "2026-06-02T11:20:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is not true.  Every service is expected to have a mechanism to disable that service.  If you don\u0027t want / don\u0027t trust a service to run, disable it.\n\nThat is functionally the exact same as a software firewall.",
      "range": {
