      "writtenOn": "2026-06-16T07:11:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The protocol filtering can be source-based - we can block or accept protocols based on the source IP/network or MAC address. \n\nExamples:\n-Block TCP protocol entirely\n-Allow TCP from 192.168.1.0/24 but block TCP from other networks\n-Allow SSH only from MAC address aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff\n-Block ICMP from specific source IPs",
      "parentUuid": "afb1b9bc_d1b05064",
