      "side": 1,
      "message": "?????  What would this mean?  Port filtering only makes sense in gateways, where sockets are being forwarded through to another entity.  the BMC doesn\u0027t forward arbitrary ranges of sockets to other devices.  If that\u0027s what you\u0027re doing, that needs added to the background that you\u0027re using the BMC as a nat/non nat gateway, which likely significantly changes this doc.",
